But there's such a cool plan that God has that if you allow him to work it out and give him time to nurture those relationships and you invest the time in those relationships,

00:11:24.576 --> 00:11:32.640
time in those relationships, you'll see the fruit come out and you'll have that aha moment when you decide to split down the road and you'll go, oh,

00:11:32.576 --> 00:11:33.536
Wow.

00:11:33.568 --> 00:11:37.600
God was here and God worked in miraculous ways.

00:11:43.136 --> 00:11:51.040
Building the kind of community that changes lives means prioritizing the relationships with the people in this group. It means being available to each other.

00:11:50.784 --> 00:11:54.752
Take a little time now and talk about community with insiders.
